미","body":"앗, 그, 그런가요!? 부, 부끄러워……\n왠지 츠쿠시 짱이 열심히 일하는 모습을 보면\n저도 모르게 흐뭇해지더라고요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf_right01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event181-06-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"듬직한 후배가 들어와서 다행이네요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event181-06-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"언니~! 츠구 짱~!\n저기 저기~ 여기 좀 와줘~!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event181-06-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"하여튼 무슨 일이야 히나?\n갈까요 하자와 씨.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"sad02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event181-06-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"츠구미","body":"네.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nnf_righ